,temperature\
[black,blue,grey,yellow],colors : colors of the three types of graduation and of the alcohol\
100,width\
[-30,40], graduation limits\
C,unit (C or F)\
raw,option word : <span class="tt">url</span>, <span class="tt">html</span> or <span class="tt">raw</span>, <span class="tt">style=left</span> \
<span class="tt">style=right</span> <span class="tt">style=leftandright</span> for the position of numbers

slib_out=Drawing of a thermometer


slib_comment=The first item of the output is: by default, the flydraw code (option word <span class="tt">raw</span>); \
the address of the generated image if the option word is <span class="tt">url</span> ; \
the html code for inserting image if the option word is the option <span class="tt">html</span>.